{"tid":772424,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"摩佬今次下台可獲1200萬鎊 總賠償金創新高！","createTime":"2018-08-08T17:36:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-08T21:03:40.000Z","uid":161790,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9dd7d8bffd19b63d6c5aa8054c427eec4d29b6f2","tid":772424,"uid":161790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T17:36:06.000Z","msg":"曼聯主教練摩連奴處在困境之中，目前他被視為最可能在新賽季下台的英超教練之一，一旦這一情況發生，摩帥將能從曼聯得到1200萬英鎊的賠償金。<br />\n<br />\n　　《太陽報》透露，如果曼聯決定在今季解僱摩帥，就不得不支付給他1200萬英鎊的賠償。從現在的情況看，這種可能性似乎不小，夏天以來，摩帥抱怨連天，尤其是批評曼聯在轉會市場上不得力，英國媒體稱他和球會執行副主席伍德禾特的關係已經出現了裂痕，而在球隊更衣室，球員們對他也有所不滿。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/09/013559_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F09%2F013559_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=92dc76c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/09/013600_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F09%2F013600_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg&h=7d7ee54f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3fa69eab6259140b5089c4d4e6badf53a1e0cb21","tid":772424,"uid":186292,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T17:48:32.000Z","msg":"解約金獵人"},{"pid":"4c5866cec468f073670ba0c70724c9af920dad34","tid":772424,"uid":31744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3fa69eab6259140b5089c4d4e6badf53a1e0cb21","tid":772424,"uid":186292,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T17:48:32.000Z","msg":"解約金獵人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T17:51:09.000Z","msg":"你半肥賓流㗎"},{"pid":"df09009a2463180eada164e583d07a1d686484f2","tid":772424,"uid":5006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T21:01:44.000Z","msg":"其實係咪啲解約金都夠過世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18ef0af45cfa93775bab1d049e499c794d4231b6